des:
Listen to this story with a timeless lesson. At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the skill. 
This Infotainment is a parable like simple story by Mutter Gottlich, a story by Dr Bheemaiah, Anil Kumar, In this story a young Bhikku monk, named Boosh discovers trans-humanism and a purpose in life, do you need a purpose in life? Have you found yours? This story may be the eye opener to your self discovery, maybe the bhikku damma may not be your belonging, but you can still be a transcendentalist, even with a practical theology, right in the middle of an urban schedule.
